# Vendored C++ engine sources. These are copied in from the repo root by
# vendor.sh and are NOT committed (to avoid duplicating the engine in the main
# repo). The publish workflow runs vendor.sh to populate this directory before
# `cargo publish`, and Cargo.toml's `include` list packages it, so the published
# crate is fully self-contained.
/vendor/

# Rust build artifacts.
/target
